metadata.name: Mia #1
metadata.description:
Wanna get on an adventure in MeStar? Follow Mia and immerse in this Blocky Metaverse! 

Mia is the first in-game avatar of MeStar. This exquisite collectible NFT art project is brought by Yoplant Labs and designed for MeStar OG family members only. 

Holders of Mia PFP will be collaboratively deciding MeStar road map. Besides that, there are also Cards, Land, Blueprints, Mystery Box, etc... Start your journey and find more available assets at mestar.me !
